data.description: Motivated seller..Welcome to your vacation home all year round! Bring friends and loved ones to enjoy happy times and gatherings around the pool/spa or playing golf. An admired gem in the gated community of Longcreek Windermere. THIS HOME HAS SO MUCH POTENTIAL. IT IS IN NEED OF SOME UPDATES.  Upon entering you will see a huge foyer that leads to a stunning living room that overlooks the pool/spa and the golf course, open floorplan, high ceilings, hardwood floors all over the living space, fireplace and plenty of natural light. Spacious formal dining room, fabulous kitchen with an eat-in area, laundry room offers plenty of cabinets. The first bedroom can be used as a second primary bedroom or in-law suite, the second room can be used as an office, the huge primary bedroom on the second floor has an overlooking balcony, walk-in closet and the primary bath has double vanities and a jacuzzi. A long aisle leads to a quiet library spot and the other two bedrooms. Oh! Let's not forget the installed "Solar" system panels that would save you A LOT of money! This is a must-see home.
